<h1>Eat Da Burgers!</h1>
<h2 class = "first">Click on a burger you would like to Devour. Once devoured it goes onto the devoured list. Want to eat more, just add a burger below!</h2>


<h2>Burgers that are not devoured!</h2>

<ul>
  {{#each burgers}}
    {{#unless devoured}}
      {{> burgers/burger devoured=true}}
    {{/unless}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Burgers that are devoured!</h2>

<ul>
  {{#each burgers}}
    {{#if devoured}}
      {{> burgers/burger devoured=false}}
    {{/if}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Add a Burger</h2>
<form class="create-form">

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="ca">BURGER NAME</label>
    <input type="text" id="ca" name="burger_name">
  </div>

